      "content": "@pklfpklf reported to us that it was possible to inject HTML into our Interviewing at Shopify site in a parameter meant for the user's name. After changing the site to properly insert this text, we closed the report as resolved. This issue was in a domain on `*.shopify.com` and did not impact our core product, so a bounty was not awarded.",
